21:02.563 --> 21:05.165
Roger, what did you do that for?!

21:05.233 --> 21:06.500
You already have the medal!

21:06.567 --> 21:08.268
I don't know.
They did it in the movie.

21:08.335 --> 21:11.003
I mean, if we're gonna go for it,
let's go for it.

